      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MT. VIEW RUPEE (6) had a tricky draw and ran well to finish third, beaten one length, (20.08) at Healesville. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Deserves serious consideration. MIGHTY HANNIBAL (2) has an excellent record over this course and distance having never missed the placings in three starts, including two wins. Was out of the placings last time (25.06) at this track in a Bottom Up - Grade 5, finishing seventh and beaten 8 lengths. Can hit the frame with the right run. VENETIAN BELLE (3) jumped from an outside draw but scored by 1.5 lengths (25.17) at Sale in T3 RSTW. Missed the placings only try here. Looks a key chance if runs up to latest figure. NICKED AGAIN (7) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.",
